 PERFORMING ARTS

 October 28 at Bharatiyam, IB 201 Sat Lake; 6 pm: EZCC presents Rupantare Rabindranath ? an evening of Tagore songs by Shinjini Acharya Majumdar and Pradip Nag. 

 October 28 at the Tollygunge Club; 7 pm: Reliance IndiaMobile, in association with Tollygunge Club and Spandan, presents Bollywood Dreams ? a music and dance extravaganza depicting various eras of Indian cinema. 

 October 29 at Kala Kunj; 6 pm: Sanchari presents Sharadiyo Rabindra Sandhya featuring an evening of Tagore songs by Suman Panthi, Suchhanda Ghosh, Debasree Biswas, Prithwish Biswas, Arindam Sadhu and Sucharita Banerjee. 

